    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/1b1b2fb2dbd2ec2cdb713a15508621c4.avif?t=1761173337\" width=776 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A psychological horror game about paranoia and anxiety.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You live alone in an apartment where strange things are happening. You can hear things in your walls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Listen close for breathing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Knock on the walls to try and find them.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/b96770c4e3539005ad3258d0787ec835.poster.avif?t=1761173337\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/b96770c4e3539005ad3258d0787ec835.webm?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/b96770c4e3539005ad3258d0787ec835.mp4?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Kill them with your axe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/e39b446311ca8aca61f42d140e001841.poster.avif?t=1761173337\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/e39b446311ca8aca61f42d140e001841.webm?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/e39b446311ca8aca61f42d140e001841.mp4?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Complete your tasks.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/3c9757dfc824f5965952e3f186aa64fa.poster.avif?t=1761173337\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/3c9757dfc824f5965952e3f186aa64fa.webm?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/3c9757dfc824f5965952e3f186aa64fa.mp4?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Go to sleep, if it is safe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/336a9dc427d359bfe71d581539744f87.poster.avif?t=1761173337\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/336a9dc427d359bfe71d581539744f87.webm?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227050/extras/336a9dc427d359bfe71d581539744f87.mp4?t=1761173337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">They will be back tomorrow.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First person interaction and exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to knock on different surfaces to listen out for hidden people.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different ways to track down and identify people.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with hardcore mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
